Author: chikinala
Text: Oh my god same. Like now I see pictures of girls that I would think look skinny and now I think they look fat. But, it’s a reality check. Those girls are not fat, this is just my ED telling me to lose more weight.

Author: speedayyyy
Text: yessss I used to be literally obese and it’s honestly quite insane how my perception of skinny has changed. Like I’m sure if I saw a picture of myself right now back when I was bigger I would consider myself skinny but looking in the mirror I still see the big fat girl despite the fact that I’ve lost literally 80 pounds. I think it’s part of the dysmorphia.
